{"tid":1112992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我沒有被煽惑","createTime":"2019-04-17T17:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T17:00:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0aab9948ade8aa5dfd1bad340c6256ceb684280c","tid":1112992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190415/20656052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656052&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=ce0438e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656052&h=cb02405b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190415/20656052</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我沒有被煽惑 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190415/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190415%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=55d5b629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「香港突發事故報料區」群組圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我沒有被煽惑。嗨各位，早晨，早晨，雖然當年被跣，滑了一大跤，之後無得做特首，但我沒有需要求情，喔，不，是陳情。我沒有敵人，不過呢，如果被我知道邊個跣我，實搵佢找數，找到2047！人有120歲命，羅局長係唔會呃人嘅呵。<br />\n<br />\n我會煽惑去煽惑？至奇！邊個煽到我？朋友嗎？我邊度有朋友啫？眾籌那個嗎？係喎，我醒起了，佢就係施政報告裏面做主角的五歲小朋友。你以為五歲小朋友財力有限公司，冇錢做眾籌？你當劉公子無到咩！<br />\n<br />\n我好似有被線劃。我從倒掛國旗的西環行埋去，個地產商就好似見到神咁，幫我掃晒高層單位，劃晒「已售」，又幫我計過數，慳到幾多印花稅。真係多謝特首，免我地N咁多個億，與她同行，夾啱天線，一手筍盤，發硬大財，真係好爽。<br />\n<br />\n我沒可能被線劃，我作為特首，條紅線係我手上，只有我劃人，冇人劃我！除咗習總！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n心 急 (尊子)"}]}